@startuml

!theme blueprint
skinparam shadowing true
hide footbox

actor User
participant "Web App" as WebApp
participant "API Server" as APIServer
participant "Database" as DB

User -> WebApp: Request page
WebApp -> APIServer: Fetch data
APIServer -> DB: Query data
DB --> APIServer: Return data
APIServer --> WebApp: Return JSON
WebApp --> User: Rendered page
@enduml
